{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_QC03_LIN_140.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x2e,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x8,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Now. Let us depart."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Umm...something's been bothering me."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x9,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "What is it?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "When that other Linca appeared,<CR>it caused a big commotion...."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "So I was wondering if you're okay with leaving Marion all by herself..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "If the other Linca appears when you're  not around..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x9,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "Thank you for worrying about us, Ayesha."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0xc,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "But there is no need to worry. I know Linca's personality the best."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0xd,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "Linca would not be satisfied with hurting Marion when I am not around."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x12,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "Linca's goal is not to hurt Marion."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "I see... If that's the case..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x9,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "If Linca were to hurt Marion, she would do it in front of me to make me feel mortified..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x9,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "That Linca would find it meaningless unless she could bathe in triumph while laughing at my failure."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "Th-That sounds scary, too..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x9,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "Besides, she may not look like it, but Marion can protect herself."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x9,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "Depending on the situation, Marion would probably defeat me."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "Wha‐!? I've never heard that before."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x195,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "It is true. I told you before,<CR>but we met on the battlefield."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0xc,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "I was captured in that battle,<CR>by Marion's hand."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0xd,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "My sword has the advantage in close combat, but it is no match for Marion's gun at medium range."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "\"Gun\"...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x11,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "Yes. Even that Linca would not be able to approach Marion without premeditation."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0xd0,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "msg_string": "And...Marion is very scary when she is mad."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x34,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x17,
            "msg_string": "Hahaha, I can kinda imagine that..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0xd2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x18,
            "msg_string": "All in all, there is no need to worry about Marion's safety. Right, Linca?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x36,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x19,
            "msg_string": "Huh...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x212,
            "name_id": 0x29,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x1a,
            "msg_string": "As one might expect, you sure do understand me very well."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x122,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x1b,
            "msg_string": "Ohhh...the other Linca!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x76,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x1c,
            "msg_string": "Have you come here for a rematch?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x212,
            "name_id": 0x29,
            "extra_id": 0x1c3,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x1d,
            "msg_string": "Of course not. Until I can measure your exact abilities, that could be disastrous."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x212,
            "name_id": 0x29,
            "extra_id": 0x1c4,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x1e,
            "msg_string": "I'm returning to my country now. I just thought I should see your face before I do so."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x212,
            "name_id": 0x29,
            "extra_id": 0x1c4,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x1f,
            "msg_string": "And, your face as well, Ayesha cupcake."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x123,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x20,
            "msg_string": "Whaaat...? M-Mine, too...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x212,
            "name_id": 0x29,
            "extra_id": 0x1c4,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x21,
            "msg_string": "Yup. You're too cute to be Linca's friend."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x212,
            "name_id": 0x29,
            "extra_id": 0x1c9,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x22,
            "msg_string": "Next time I visit, I'd like for you to be my friend, too."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x124,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x23,
            "msg_string": "Eh, heh heh... What should I do? Umm..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x24,
            "msg_string": "Well, if you can skip all that scary stuff, I'd love to..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x212,
            "name_id": 0x29,
            "extra_id": 0x1c4,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x25,
            "msg_string": "No can do. It's impossible not to tease something that you find cute, am I right?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x26,
            "msg_string": "Kyaaah!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x77,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x27,
            "msg_string": "If you even try to lay a finger on Ayesha, I will..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x212,
            "name_id": 0x29,
            "extra_id": 0x1c5,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x28,
            "msg_string": "Ooh, scary. I guess I better leave quietly today, after all..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x212,
            "name_id": 0x29,
            "extra_id": 0x19c,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x29,
            "msg_string": "Well then, see ya later."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x77,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x2a,
            "msg_string": "...I still have much to experience."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x77,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x2b,
            "msg_string": "I am...a sword to protect my loved ones, Marion and Ayesha."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x7a,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x2c,
            "msg_string": "No matter what happens, no matter what kinds of enemies attack... A single sword that never breaks..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x7b,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x2d,
            "msg_string": "I need to become a sword like that!"
        }
    ]
}